    <h3 class="text-center font-weight-bold">GC Services’ Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p>Effective Date: January 2020</p>
    <div>
        <p>At GC Services, we are committed to safeguarding the privacy and security of your personal information. We want you to know how we may collect, use, share, and keep information about you and the steps we take to ensure your privacy and security are protected. This Privacy Policy applies to your personal information collected by GC Services, both through GC Services’ websites and offline, in accordance with the terms described below.</p>
        <p>For purposes of this Privacy Policy, personal information means information that directly or indirectly identifies a particular individual, such as the name, mailing address, email address, telephone number, social security number, and other identifiable information. When otherwise non-identifiable information is directly or indirectly associated with personal information, the resulting combination of information is also treated as personal information.</p>
    </div>

