        <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Methods Used to Collect Your Personal Information:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>You may provide personal information directly to us either over the phone or in writing (including electronically);</li>
            <li>Your personal information may be shared with us through one of our clients;</li>
            <li>Your personal information may be supplied to us by one of our trusted service providers.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We may also gather personal information about you online if you:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Visit or use our website(s) or applications, including through the use of technologies such as cookies;</li>
            <li>Receive or reply to electronic communications from us;</li>
            <li>Submit forms to us electronically; or</li>
            <li>Register, log into, or make changes to your account information.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Personal information collected about you online and in other ways may be combined.  Any combined information may be used, shared, and kept as described below.  Combined information will be used, shared, and kept in the same manner as if the personal information had not been combined.</p>
    </div>

